User Permissions
- android.permission.CAMERA We use camera phone to take photo support feature edit photo and make video.
- android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE , android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE to get photos from gallery and store videos result to sdcard.
- android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO use camera phone to take short video support feature edit and make video
- android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE use for Admob Ads SDK( Google Admob Ads). In our app have contain Ads.
